HeliosX-Job-JSON version 1.00
=============================

HeliosX::Job::JSON is a Helios::Job subclass allowing you to specify 
Helios job arguments in JSON format instead of Helios's default XML 
format.  

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Helios 2.80 or later
    JSON::Tiny 0.49 or later

